                    <div class="md:text-right pr-8">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700">3000 BC - 1300 AD</h4>
                        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-indigo-600 uppercase mb-2">Word of Mouth</div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-serif">Employment worked on referrals. Someone in your village recommended a cousin. Trust was inherent.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white timeline-dot"></div>
