                    <div class="md:block hidden"></div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-800 rounded-full border-4 border-white timeline-dot"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pl-8">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700">1400s - 1800s</h4>
                        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800 uppercase mb-2">The Broadside</div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-serif">Paper manufacturing allowed for public notices. Ads were nailed to posts and piers. The birth of "Help Wanted".</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20 relative items-center timeline-item visible-content">
                    <div class="md:text-right pr-8">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700">1999</h4>
                        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-purple-600 uppercase mb-2">The Digital Explosion</div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-serif">Monster.com launches. Internet replaces newspapers. Ads are no longer charged by the line.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-purple-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white timeline-dot"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pl-8 md:block hidden"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 4 -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative items-center timeline-item visible-content">
                    <div class="md:block hidden"></div>
                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white timeline-dot"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pl-8">
                        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700">2007 - Present</h4>
                        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-red-600 uppercase mb-2">The Aggregation Era</div>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-serif">Indeed, SmashFly, and 100,000+ job boards. Volume explodes. Quality plummets.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: THE DATA (THE PROBLEM) -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">The Technology Paradox</h3>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Technology should improve communication. In recruitment, it undermined it.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <!-- Chart 1: Explosion of Boards -->
